trans-unit.source: Contains information about an ink gesture.
trans-unit.target: 包含筆墨筆勢的相關資訊。

trans-unit.source: A GestureRecognitionResult contains an <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture> and the level of likeliness that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> correctly identified the gesture.
trans-unit.target: 包含 GestureRecognitionResult<xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>和 likeliness 層級的<xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer>正確識別手勢。</xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A> property to determine the level of likeliness that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> correctly identified the gesture.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A>屬性來判斷 likeliness 的層級的<xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer>正確識別手勢。</xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A>
取得可辨識的筆墨筆勢。

trans-unit.source: Gets the level of confidence that the <xref href="System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer"></xref> has in the recognition of the gesture.
trans-unit.target: 取得的信心層級<xref href="System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer"></xref>中的筆勢辨識。
